msgctxt "56"
msgid "Attention should be paid to the degree to which the cue stick is drawn back, as it affects the power of the shot."
msgstr "Es necesario prestar atención la distancia que uno estira el palo hacia atrás, ya que afectará a la potencia del tiro."

msgctxt "68"
msgid "Moving it straight towards you is the secret to a steady shot."
msgstr "Moverlo recto hacia ti es la clave para un disparo recto."

